@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ecburq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.08
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.45 + tmp + 0.22) - (v2 + 0.67 - v0 + 0.60)) / v1)
    v1 = (wp.exp(0.91) * ((v1 + 0.39 * v2 + 0.28) - 0.44))
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.41) + wp.exp(v0 + 0.85)))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.44 - (v2 + 0.07 * tmp + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
